newpath
.9 printscale div setlinewidth
0 30 moveto
 80 10  90 78 110 75 curveto
150 69 150 90 180 90 curveto
230 90 228 32 240 30 curveto
%320 10 330 78 350 75 curveto		% carries the graph into
stroke						% the next day
grestore

% axes
newpath
0 0 moveto
255 0 lineto
rightarrow
0 0 moveto
0 105 lineto
uparrow
fill
0 0 moveto 
4 {hscale} repeat
0 0 moveto 
3 {vscale} repeat
stroke

